Package jcuda.jcurand Description

Contains the classes of JCurand.

This package contains classes that are related to JCurand. The main class is the JCurand class, which provides all method bindings for CURAND, the NVIDIA CUDA random number generator library.

Please consult your CURAND library documentation for more information about how to use this API.
